item.title: Data Visualization of Shoes Data
item.description: I will display all the visualization that I made here since Github unable to display my data visualization :smile: Objective 1: To determine the frequency of customer membership status purchases by product gender Objective 2: To identify the quantity purchases by gender and product category Objective 3: To identify quantity purchases by gender and product brand Objective 4: To determine total sales by agent id name and product brand Objective 5: To analyse total sales by date We can move the date slider to our preference date
